a.xlink:title: class CreditsCommand used to print the credits of the game
class DropCommand used to make the player drop an Item
class EatCommand used to make the player eat an object.
class GiveCommand used to make the Player give an Item
class GoCommand used to make the player go to a given Room.
class HelpCommand used to print the help
class InventoryCommand used to print the player's inventory
class LookCommand used to show information about the current Room or a given Item ...
class QuitCommand used to quit the game
class TakeCommand used to make the Player take an Item
class TalkCommand used to talk to a Character
class TestCommand used to test series of commands
class BackCommand used to go back in a previous Room.
class BeamerCommand used to teleport into a remembered room
